ho won a raffle and performed some of his solo music, including an extended version of his song \\\"Super Tuna\\\".\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jin, 31, has announced plans to release more solo music and is scheduled to appear on a variety show later this year.\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1276, \"end\": 1279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.247042908434127e-21, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am working on recording music and filming variety shows.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am trying to focus on my main job while showing my face as much as possible,\\\" he wrote on online fan platform Weverse.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The results will be out in a few months, so please wait a little longer.\\\"\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans excited to see him act, however, had their expectations dashed.\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not have any plans to act.\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sorry about that,\\\" Jin said.\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1775, \"end\": 1778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.247042908434127e-21, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The summer Olympics are scheduled to take place from 26 July till 11 August.\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The c